{"tid":1344286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明白勇武防衛重要 依加需要你地","createTime":"2019-07-21T21:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:18:49.000Z","uid":264368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"baaa08edb0eb9d910ea67187fae624183047c9f8","tid":1344286,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:29:58.000Z","msg":"首先要有冇鬼既Group <br />\n<br />\n方法就係:<br />\n只傳確切肯定為和理非或勇武義士既朋友<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但首先需要一班願意互相驗證身份既巴絲</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n願因同目的大概如下:<br />\n<br />\n鑑於目前運動中存在多個資訊傳遞既缺陷同問題，<br />\n有需要完善溝通凝聚力量促進行動成效。<br />\n只屬秘密資訊溝通平台，並非大台，<br />\n以改善行動策略 、資源分配、安全考慮等，例如：<br />\n<br />\n行動：<br />\n避免資訊混亂<br />\n有效統計己方力量<br />\n事前或現場決議、策略溝通<br />\n配合進行更有效策略<br />\n例如突擊、包抄、聲東擊西<br />\n<br />\n資源：<br />\n確保資源用得其所<br />\n有效分配人力物力<br />\n減少資源浪費<br />\n<br />\n安全：<br />\n可信即時現場資訊<br />\n現場身份調查確認<br />\n秘密暗號或手勢<br />\n防止行動資料外洩"},{"pid":"a8814e4436fa18900eeeb88a5311004e937cd525","tid":1344286,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054b07fc6be3224cb468f92a38970592bcd022c0","tid":1344286,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T21:36:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b169a7f77296f356cb63e0f946214e318291990f","tid":1344286,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}